      rating: '5', author: 'Angela T.', date: '2025-02-10',
    },
    {
      body: "We had a small hall bathroom updated in our Fremont cottage — new tub surround, vanity, toilet, and LVP floor. Quick 2-week turnaround. Looks clean and modern without going overboard on budget.",
      rating: '5', author: 'Dave R.', date: '2024-10-14',
    },
    {
      body: "Solid work on our Kirkland ensuite. Frameless glass shower enclosure turned out beautiful. Only knock is the tile delivery was delayed a few days, but they communicated the schedule change right away.",
      rating: '4', author: 'Priya N.', date: '2024-07-29',
    },
    {
      body: "Renovated both bathrooms in our Bellevue tri-level. Master got a full luxury treatment — freestanding tub, walk-in shower with dual showerheads, heated floor, backlit mirror. Guest bath got a simpler but still modern refresh. They managed both simultaneously and finished in 5 weeks. The tile work in both is absolutely flawless.",
      rating: '5', author: 'James & Amy W.', date: '2025-03-05',
