    {
      body: "Steam shower installation in our Sammamish home. Full tile enclosure with glass door, built-in bench, eucalyptus holders, and a Kohler steam generator. The waterproofing and vapor barrier work was extensive — they clearly know what they're doing with steam systems. It's our own private spa now.",
