    },
    {
      body: "Tub-to-shower conversion in our Redmond townhouse. Removed the old garden tub nobody used and put in a spacious walk-in with dual showerheads, a fold-down teak bench, and three niches. The drain placement and floor slope are perfect — no standing water at all. Great work.",
