    },
    {
      body: "Had them build a custom island with seating on one side and storage on the other. Cherry wood, shaker style, with integrated wine rack and pull-out trash. Took about 4 weeks from measurement to install. Only issue was one drawer was slightly misaligned — they adjusted it same day.",
