    },
    {
      body: "Complete custom cabinet kitchen for our Woodinville craftsman. Inset doors, concealed hinges, dovetail drawers, and they matched the existing trim profile in our 1920s home. 25 cabinets total including a built-in hutch. The level of detail is remarkable — these aren't box store cabinets.",
