  'flooring-installation': [
    {
      body: "LVP throughout our entire Renton rambler — about 1,400 sq ft of COREtec. Waterproof, looks like real wood, and they included quarter round trim. Transitions between rooms are seamless. Three guys knocked it out in 2.5 days. Very happy.",
