      body: "Full accessibility remodel of both bathrooms in our Burien ranch for my parents. Curbless showers with fold-down seats, grab bars that match the fixtures, comfort-height toilets, and anti-slip tile. The attention to safety details was impressive — they even adjusted the lighting to be brighter without being harsh.",
